Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  塞茲邊境的無人之地出現了羅馬大軍？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的槍聲是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到羅馬兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我隊將與展開於國防線的第一第三師團匯合…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我就要開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐  請讓部下們退到曉時堡轄外
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TITLE-------------------
